{"lang": "zh_CN", "eventid": "act50side", "eventName": "泡影苍霆", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "TD-5", "avgTag": "行动前", "storyName": "只能成功，不能失败", "storyInfo": "面对兽潮，众人制定好应对策略，月见夜和空爆外出诱敌，梓兰和宝巫迦留守城内，一切看似顺利......", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g1_impermanence_street", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2110_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t将军，陛下，你们终于回来了！", "name": "武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2110_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "情况如何？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2110_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t启禀陛下！野兽还在源源不断地从“御轮”的方向涌来！它们......它们根本杀不完！", "name": "武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2110_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2110_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t将军这些年建造的防线起到了作用，但是，被攻破恐怕是时间问题。", "name": "武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2110_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......辛苦了。传令下去，让他们再坚持一段时间，不能让防线崩溃，我和陛下会有办法。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2110_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t是！我们相信您和陛下！", "name": "武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2110_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夸下海口，要是做不到该怎么办？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "团队最重士气，有信心重于一切。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "说得轻巧，单纯的防守只是在用人命拖延时间，是慢性死亡。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今“雷之主”已经是兽潮的首领，空爆小姐说得没错，在确保都城安全的前提下，先将它杀死依然是最好的选择。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白你的意思，陛下。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但兽潮来势汹涌，我们必须先解决眼下的麻烦。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾会亲自带兵消灭兽潮，吾等狩猎之国的子民，死也应当死在狩猎之中。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不可。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下或许可以杀十头，甚至百头野兽，但根据斥候的观察，兽潮源源不断。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你有什么办法？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......首先，我要说一个悲观的结论，想靠泡影国现在的力量正面抵挡兽潮恐怕是不可能的。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若是再给我三十年准备，或许我能够培养出能够抵御这场兽潮的部队。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾知道，眼下的吾等，做不到正面抵挡。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没错，我们必须主动出击，将兽潮分流。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎么分？按你的说法，我们的兵力本就捉襟见肘，你这么做无异于将我们本就脆弱的防线一分为二。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白你的顾虑，梓兰小姐。所以，这次行动并非强攻，而是智取。我们有一个......独一无二的诱饵。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "诱饵？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#10$2"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "刚被我们讨伐的“异兽”熔火蜗，它的尸体。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用它的尸体？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没错。梓兰小姐，你们也见识过“诅咒”了。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一种不祥的能量，而被“诅咒”侵蚀的野兽，会本能地被更强大的“诅咒”源所吸引，如同飞蛾扑火。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，宝巫迦不是已经把它的“诅咒”吸收了吗？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾只是吸收了必要的能量来启动“御轮”......它身上的“诅咒”并未完全消除。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而它的尸体，对那些被“诅咒”侵染的野兽而言，是无法抗拒的“盛宴”。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用狩猎对象来吸引狩猎对象，这倒是很符合猎人的风格喵。", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$2"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，要把它们引到哪里去？在平原上，我们跑不过无穷无尽的兽潮喵。", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$4"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "月见夜的手指点在地图上的一处狭长地带，那里是都城外的竹林。"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城东数里外，这片竹林的地表之下，有一片巨大的空洞，是古代地下河干涸后留下的遗迹。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是想......", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没错。我们可以派一支精锐部队作为诱饵，用“异兽”熔火蜗的尸体，将兽潮的主力吸引至这片竹林，然后......", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用斑弥罗特制的炸药，引爆地表，制造大规模塌陷，让它们掉下去，摔死它们。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "计策听来可行，但是......为什么这里有一处空洞，吾却全然不知？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这里......", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$2"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等喵，这不是前代陛下——", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$4"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......没错，这处空洞，正是“雷之主”的巢穴。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......？！", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这正是陛下这些年遍历周围都没法找到“雷之主”巢穴的原因。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本不愿意将此处告诉陛下，但是，事急从权。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "由吾亲自去。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“异兽”熔火蜗是吾狩猎的，它身上的“诅咒”与吾的巫女之力有所感应，由吾拖动尸体，吸引的效果最好。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恕我......无法遵命，陛下。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#7$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "月见夜！吾乃一国之主，亦是泡影国最强的猎人之一！", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "难道说，到了现在你还担心吾会因为冲动而去挑战“雷之主”吗？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "过去十年，无论“雷之主”暗中在做什么，它没有为我们带来灭顶之灾。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这给了我们安宁的时间。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕这份安宁是屈辱的，只要它是安宁，我就愿意死守它，为此，被认为懦弱也好，保守也罢，我都无所谓。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，只有一点我希望您能相信我，这些年来，我做的一切，都是为了给您铺好杀死“雷之主”的道路。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，我们现在还不知道“雷之主”究竟如何引发了这场异变。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "还不是时候。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这句话吾已经听过太多遍了，究竟什么时候才是对的时候？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "为什么你总是想要为吾安排一切？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......因为，我见过您没有见过的东西。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下留在都城里，就是对民心和士气最好的鼓舞。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今的泡影国需要您。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你总是这样。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰小姐，请你留在都城中协助陛下。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用你说我也打算这么做。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，你确定那个地点的地层一定能被炸开吗？万一失败，诱饵部队就会被兽潮彻底淹没。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信斑弥罗。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也可以帮忙！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......空爆确实是眼下最强的单兵战力。月见夜，你带上她，还有义经，一切按你的计划行事。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收到！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyD_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_dog_voice1", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（充满战意的吼叫）", "name": "义经"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyD_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "政宗，你和我留下，协助陛下守城。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没问题喵！我会看好陛下的喵！", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "月见夜。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "臣在。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#10$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......活着回来。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#5$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g2_impermanence_room", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_swordwhoosh", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_swordwhoosh", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，陛下，我知道你现在心情很不爽。", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是能不能不要在我家里空挥？", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾在宫里待不下去。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我家里就会心情愉快点吗？！", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你和月见夜关系不差，看着你挥，会让吾解气一点。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和那家伙关系可算不上好。", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也觉得奇怪，堂堂月见夜将军，为什么好像只跟你关系还不错？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "为什么你也理所当然地出现在我家，我家是什么游乐园吗？！", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在宫里也有点待不下去，剩下认识的地方也只有这里了。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啧。", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十年前，我还是个学徒，那家伙也只是前代陛下的跟屁虫。", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的师父加入了前代陛下的远征队，因为被受“诅咒”的野兽袭击死了，前代陛下后来也失踪了。", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "从那之后，他就时不时会来找我，还美其名曰同病相怜。哼，我是不觉得有什么同病相怜。", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不恨“雷之主”？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恨啊，所以我才一直在研究新的装备，等着有一天有人用我做的武器杀了“雷之主”。", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......原来你是认真的？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我从来也没说过我不是认真的，只是大家都不相信罢了。", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也只有月见夜那家伙会一直鼓励我，但也就这样了，他会帮我，我却帮不上他，这算不上朋友。", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "朋友可不是这么算的。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，宝巫迦，总是待在这里也不是办法。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们一起去看看外面有没有什么需要帮助的地方。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}